Dear [Employee Name],

We're thrilled to be assisting you with your relocation to [City name]!  We're making excellent progress on your move and wanted to confirm your upcoming phone consultation.

During this call, we'll discuss your housing preferences in more detail and answer any questions you may have about the available properties and the relocation process. We're committed to making this transition as smooth as possible for you.

We look forward to speaking with you soon!

Sincerely,

The [Relocation Company Name] Team
